But if you haven't‚Äîand even if you¬†have!‚ÄîI hope you'll take a few minutes to enjoy it with me. Here's the idea: Every matrix corresponds to a graph. So simple! But we can get a lot of mileage out of it.To start, I'll be a little more precise: every matrix corresponds to a¬†weighted bipartite graph.
